msgid ""
"Yāni, bhikkhave, mānusakāni soḷasa vassasatāni, paranimmitavasavattīnaṃ "
"devānaṃ eso eko rattindivo."
msgstr ""
"Sixteen hundred years in the human realm is one day and night for the Gods "
"Who Control the Creations of Others."

msgctxt "an8.42:9.2"
msgid "Tāya rattiyā tiṃsarattiyo māso."
